# CLAUDE-LOCAL.md — Python Project Additions
# Copy to: <project>/CLAUDE-LOCAL.md
# This file is appended to the generated CLAUDE.md

## Python Environment

- **Python**: 3.12
- **Virtual env**: `.venv/` (activate: `source .venv/bin/activate`)
- **Package manager**: pip + pyproject.toml
- **Linting**: ruff (`ruff check .`)
- **Type checking**: mypy strict (`mypy .`)
- **Formatting**: ruff format (`ruff format .`)

## Project-Specific Commands

```bash
# Run all tests
pytest

# Run with coverage
pytest --cov=src --cov-report=term-missing

# Type check
mypy src/

# Lint + format
ruff check . --fix && ruff format .
```

## Architecture Notes

<!-- Uncomment the section that matches your project type -->

<!-- CONTENT / CREATIVE PROJECT
- Content generation pipelines in `src/generators/`
- Templates in `src/templates/`
- No strict layering — focus on typing and test coverage
-->

<!-- DATA PIPELINE PROJECT
- Pipeline definitions in `src/pipelines/`
- Data models in `src/models/`
- No layer enforcement — typing checks on all modules
-->

<!-- API PROJECT (default)
- Standard layered architecture: domain → services → api
- Repository pattern for data access
- Pydantic models for validation at boundaries
-->

